This paper deals with image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves normalization and convolution, which are also common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also includes experiments and evaluations, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
